message: MEN OF CRU! I have a friend who is looking for a place to live this coming Spring semester, preferably in a house. He's going to be going to community college, moving from Iowa, so he wants an opportunity to meet new people and get plugged in to a ministry. In addition, he is potentially looking for a place to live next year and loves the idea of being in a house. Is there anything open at least for next semester? Shoot me a message if you think you can help him out! Thanks :)
